once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree ,which was on the banks of a river.In the same 
forest there lived a crocodile and his wife . one day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under
the tree .the kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. then the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as 
he loved them . as days passed by the crocodile and monkey became good friends.
